quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,Alif Laam Miim
  2,2,"Icyo ni igitabo (Qur’an) kidashidi- kanywaho, kikaba umuyoboro ku batinya Allah"
  2,3,"Babandi bemera ibitagaragara (byahanuwe), bagahozaho amase- ngesho (Swalat) kandi bagatangamu byo twabahaye"
  2,4,"Ni nabo bemera ibyo (wowe Muhamadi) wahishuriwe (Qur’an n’imigenzo y’intumwa), bakanemera ibyahishuwe mbere yawe (ibitabo byahishuriwe intumwa zakubanjirije), ndetse bakemera imperuka badashidikanya"
  2,5,"Abo ni bo bari mu nzira iboneye yagenwe na Nyagasani wabo, kandi ni bo bakiranutsi"